OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry and breezy across much of
OL,6,Fthe region, with early light rain in
OL,7,Fthe south soon clearing away during
OL,8,Fthe morning. Plenty of prolonged sunny
OL,9,Fspells, especially through the
OL,10,Fafternoon. Temperatures slightly above
OL,11,Faverage.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA very pleasant evening with
OL,14,Fwidespread sunshine and easing winds
OL,15,Ffor many, followed by a mostly calm
OL,16,Fand clear night.
OL,17,
OL,18,CFriday:FVariable cloud on Friday, but
OL,19,Fplenty of sunny spells through the
OL,20,Fday. Warm to very warm in the sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
